{"tid":124835,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾偉雄：七名同事執勤時「可能犯咗啲錯誤」","createTime":"2017-02-18T03:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T09:00:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb3b0de1034e5350e6a674c9fb4a5c1c3703731","tid":124835,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/74206.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F74206.png&h=fbc6409e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七名警員因為毆打前公民黨成員曾健超罪成，全部判監兩年兼不得假釋，更可能被革職失去長俸退休金；2014年佔領運動期間任警務處處長、現已退休的前「一哥」曾偉雄接受《明報》訪問時指心情沉重，強調如7名警員上訴，其他同袍會全力協助。<br />\n<br />\n被問及對判刑的看法，曾偉雄指自己與很多同事﹙警員﹚心情均非常沉重，因同事在執勤期間「可能犯咗啲錯誤。」對於警隊沒為警員執勤期間犯刑責認錯是否姑息犯事警員，曾回應「不要再講這個問題」，又指應向「現任嗰啲」查詢，自己只是以市民身份回應。<br />\n<br />\n2014年佔領運動期間，前「一哥」曾偉雄曾向警員稱「你哋冇做錯到」，接受傳媒訪問時形容警察如慈母般保護學生。"},{"pid":"57aa2596edfa23520fec87e1065c41304f730342","tid":124835,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ff6a85456595bf47d0824977fcd2e189b6bb9c","tid":124835,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9845b0485667245d3f8daf33c57f09892a1d85","tid":124835,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想屌問呢位影撚衰LSOB既盧犬：<br />\n<br />\n1. 出埋Judgement同Penalty而實際未有任何FormalAppeal，咁都唔係玩完法律程序？？你呢位執法CP厄飯食架？？<br />\n<br />\n2. 你同3萬隻義工黎架？？？你要睇3萬隻頭，就當幾百萬出你糧既透明呀？？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=